latestPosts.caption:
A day that brought vision, craft, and creativity together— #CanonDeepDive MasterClass, Gurugram edition!

Wedding filmmakers and photographers came together for a one-of-a-kind learning experience led by none other than Siddharth Sharma, Founder of House on the Clouds (@thehouseontheclouds). From shooting on a live set to sharing his real-time creative process, Siddharth opened the doors to how storytelling meets execution.

The day was packed with:
* A hands-on shoot session with Siddharth
* Deep dives into post-production, lighting, and sound
* Interactive exchanges, questions, and insights
* Exploration of Canon’s latest RF system cameras and lenses

A huge shoutout to our technology partners @aputureindia, @sennheiser_in, and @eizoindia—your support made the experience even more powerful.

This was just the beginning. Hyderabad, you're up next!

#CanonDeepDive #CanonIndia #SiddharthSharma #HouseOnTheClouds #WeddingFilmmakers #CanonPhotography #CanonVideography #ClickWithCanon #FilmmakingMasterclass #DelightingYouAlways #CANwithCanon

Wedding Filmmakers & Photographers – This One’s for You! 🎥📸

Introducing the one of its kind, Canon Deep Dive, an exclusive learning experience with Siddharth Sharma, Founder of House on the Clouds @thehouseontheclouds. This isn’t just another masterclass—it’s a rare opportunity to watch Siddharth in action as he shoots LIVE, breaking down his creative process in real-time.

What makes this different?

Live Set Experience: Watch Siddharth direct and capture in real-time
Interactive Q&A: Join an open house with Siddharth
Behind-the-Scenes: Explore post-production insights
Technology Sessions: Discover cutting-edge workflows 
Hands-On: Try Canon’s latest RF system cameras and lenses
 
📍 Gurugram – 4th April’25
📍 Hyderabad – 13th April’25
